{"tid":534631,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人最愛日劇原來是這 10 部，2017 年滿意度排行榜大公開","createTime":"2018-01-20T04:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T19:11:24.000Z","uid":9573,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"4b75106951fefc7d6bf25de5ec02ce3869261bd5","tid":534631,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee59e0e57.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee59e0e57.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=8883a559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依照不同星期、時段，每一季都有約莫 40 部的日劇播放，算下來一年就超過百部了，正因為如此，在如此激烈的競爭下，要成為年度最受觀眾歡迎的可不容易，日本網站「テレビウォッチャー」排除了深夜劇，每日蒐集了 2400 人的滿意度調查，經過一年後統計出 2017 年最滿意度最高的 80 部日劇，想確認自己有沒有漏看了哪一部，看這排行榜就對了！<br />\n<br />\nNo.10 《CRISIS 公安機動搜查隊特搜班》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee59e6130.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee59e6130.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=71bf76a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由小栗旬主演的警匪片，加上和編劇金城一紀的黃金組合，讓不少人光是在開播前便引頸期盼，故事描述由 5 位各有身懷絕技的探員組成了「特搜班」，專門解決各種警察難處理的危機，扎實的打鬥戲是最為人看得津津樂道的部分，每個角色鮮明的個性也讓故事更有看頭。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lsDP9WMS4HQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlsDP9WMS4HQ&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=2e2e5324\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lsDP9WMS4HQ</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.9 《小巨人》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee5ab8dcb.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee5ab8dcb.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=f0ebf1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來自《半澤直樹》的團隊組合，導演田中健太和製作人伊與田英德、飯田和孝，還有八津宏幸的腳本協力，劇情模式也有些類似，《小巨人》主角長谷川博已發現警政背後的貪污醜聞，之後就是小蝦米對抗大鯨魚的故事了，因為劇情高潮迭起又能帶來正面能量頗受好評，演員們淋漓盡致的演技更是無話可說。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m3EUxptr208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm3EUxptr208&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bffb6118\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m3EUxptr208</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.8 《派遣女醫 X 5》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee5adcce8.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee5adcce8.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=d6d695c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從 2012 年開始播放的系列電視醫療劇，卡在 2017 年底上檔的第五季擁有相當不錯的成績，在故事中凡事零失敗的米倉涼子，這回出現了身體不適的危機，也讓大結局觀看人數大增，打敗了前面四季，獲得了全系列最高的即時收視率。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ryW_UOAV1Dg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FryW_UOAV1Dg&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5536a306\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ryW_UOAV1Dg</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.7 《小荳荳》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee5a1accd.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee5a1accd.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=20a11e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前 10 名中唯一上榜的午間劇，講述日本第一位女演員黑柳徹子的故事，先前 NHK 出品過《小荳荳電視台》，找來滿島光主演，這回則是由朝日電視台找來清野菜名詮釋黑柳徹子，雖然只有短短 20 分鐘，不過頗受午間時段的婦女們喜愛，拿下第 7 名。<br />\n<br />\nNo.6 《澪之料理帖》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee5aba440.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee5aba440.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=3f4f2659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同名暢銷小說改編的週六時代劇，時空背景落在江戶時代，第一部女主角是由北川景子飾演，於 2012 年播出，2017 年的第二部則是由黑木華主演，溫馨的劇情加上善解人意的女主角，還有一道道讓人看了口水直流的江戶料理，都讓本劇獲得好評價。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KkWsgppii-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKkWsgppii-A&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4a0dd3c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KkWsgppii-A</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.5 《Code Blue 3》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee5ad2a70.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee5ad2a70.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=f35db4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想當初官方宣佈《Code Blue》要出全新一季可是引起了不小的話題，畢竟 5 位卡司全到齊，再外加隔了 7 年之久，包括了人氣直直升的新垣結衣與山下智久、戶田惠梨香，這部片自然成為了收視保證，今年暑假還會有劇場版上映！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0fEbFvyJwS8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0fEbFvyJwS8&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9e110106\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0fEbFvyJwS8</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.4 《產科醫鴻鳥 2》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee5a53752.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee5a53752.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=9fd7a514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n改編自 2012 年開始連載的同名漫畫《產科醫鴻鳥》，2015 年第一次改編便獲得廣大迴響，這回第二部開播，還找來了《月薪嬌妻》剛播畢的男主角星野源當配角，劇情透過每一次的生產來彰顯生命的可貴，是一部既溫馨又催淚的電視劇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y3k0vWSXyfw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy3k0vWSXyfw&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=38917453\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y3k0vWSXyfw</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.3 《謊言戰爭》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAuFKAI.img?h=449&amp;w=728&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=434&amp;y=193\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAuFKAI.img%3Fh%3D449%26w%3D728%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D434%26y%3D193&h=58b6952d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卡司包括了草彅剛、藤木直人、水原希子，故事描述主角草彅剛家破人亡，長大後成為一名詐欺犯，遇上當年殺害家人的兇手準備展開復仇，水原希子則是飾演她的拍檔，中鋒基奧特又受傷倦勤，中場靈魂奧斯爾亦上陣成疑，僅餘的前鋒拿卡錫迪亦陷入球荒。故事劇情充滿不知是真是假的角色對白，讓觀眾們看了覺得十分爽快！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Olb5XZeA2ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOlb5XZeA2ts&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=126f5a4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Olb5XZeA2ts</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.2 《反轉》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee5aca2b5.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee5aca2b5.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=dc98f6cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講述上了軌道的生活因為一封信開始掀起了波瀾，牽扯出 10 年前的好友身亡案，才發現大家都有著不可告人的秘密，進而讓目前的生活有了 180 度的大轉變，觀眾的心也跟著劇情峰迴路轉，留下深刻印象。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J6aLc3u3SIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ6aLc3u3SIo&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0c7cee52\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J6aLc3u3SIo</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.1 《陸王》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/74877/5a5eee5ad7093.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F74877%2F5a5eee5ad7093.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=16477a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二部編劇八津宏幸上榜的日劇，男主角役所廣司鮮少參與電視劇演出，故事描述日本傳統足袋面臨即將淘汰的命運，必須要與時俱進做出改變。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4tK-8ztSXwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4tK-8ztSXwU&d=CJoPyNSCXcazU8h9H4m76y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=df6ab0ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4tK-8ztSXwU</a><br />\n除了重量級的役所廣司，飾演兒子的山崎賢人表現也格外亮眼，十集平均創下了 16% 的高收視率，完結篇更是有 20% 之高。"},{"pid":"95179c0fcdcf64bb8c750bd53d474e5d7e0c6140","tid":534631,"uid":12176,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"個人覺得陸王實至名歸，但係反轉真係吹大左嘅垃圾...又拖劇情結局又唔爆，點解口碑咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a98214582872e2315ba4dfc3f86747a20c1e1c8","tid":534631,"uid":158660,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:39:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61404c7bebdaeab1b2408b5aba71b5bff8e8f35b","tid":534631,"uid":38102,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"反轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n10部入面淨係睇過3部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bde31dd7a34ab70639a9e84c565befc91420fb","tid":534631,"uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"做咩有傑志睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f956bd933160c1ebd0a36d00c38507a671e61b","tid":534631,"uid":47311,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"卡司包括了草彅剛、藤木直人、水原希子，故事描述主角草彅剛家破人亡，長大後成為一名詐欺犯，遇上當年殺害家人的兇手準備展開復仇，水原希子則是飾演她的拍檔，中鋒基奧特又受傷倦勤，中場靈魂奧斯爾亦上陣成疑，僅餘的前鋒拿卡錫迪亦陷入球荒。故事劇情充滿不知是真是假的角色對白，讓觀眾們看了覺得十分爽快！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩料"},{"pid":"31cc78df5a01e71da6ec2e6e67e36940c9dc170a","tid":534631,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a8bde31dd7a34ab70639a9e84c565befc91420fb","tid":534631,"uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"做咩有傑志睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d91df0f3972c7da074b5a52b3fbe37aeef321e0","tid":534631,"uid":99908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62f956bd933160c1ebd0a36d00c38507a671e61b","tid":534631,"uid":47311,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"卡司包括了草彅剛、藤木直人、水